1. Send POST /api/auctions
2. Authorization: Bearer <auctioneer_token>
3. Body: {code; name; assetType; startingPrice; bidIncrement; auctionStartAt; auctionEndAt; ...}

1. Send POST /api/auctions
2. Authorization: Bearer <admin_token>
3. Body: {auctionStartAt: future_date; auctionEndAt: earlier_than_start_date}

1. Send PUT /api/auctions/:id
2. Authorization: Bearer <admin_token>
3. Body: {auctionStartAt: newDate; auctionEndAt: newDate}

1. Send POST /api/manual-bid
2. Authorization: Bearer <bidder_token>
3. Body: {auctionId: 'uuid'; amount: 5000000}

1. Send POST /api/auction-finalization/handle-winner-default
2. Authorization: Bearer <admin_token>
3. Body: {auctionId: 'uuid'; reason: 'Failed to pay within deadline'}

